id: pm-j8z6
title: Reconcile linked-file ownership after source and test relocations
description: Audit and reconcile stale linked-file rows plus currently unowned source/test artifacts reported by pm validate --check-files. Use pm CLI validation hints and linked-artifact commands so the tracker reflects current code ownership without manual storage edits.
